snippet.title: Super Donkey Kong 99
snippet.description:
This is a pirate game for the Sega Genesis, featuring graphics from the Donkey Kong Country games.
Save states only used in between levels, with the exception of the final level, where there is a barrel that usually kills me, and I have no idea how to get past it without saving.
I also had to switch from Gens to Fusion halfway through because one of the bosses doesn't work on that emulator.
